# Chocolate Pots #

## Ingredients 

- 100g dark chocolate
- 250ml double cream
- 40g muscovado sugar
- vanilla
- 1 egg

## Method

1. blend chocolate
2. cream, sugar in pan and bring to the boil
3. pour into blender leave for 1 minute
4. switch on and add egg for 20 seconds
5. pour into ramekins and chill (2hours or preferably overnight)
